{"title":"南海明珠","authors":["胡弦"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海明珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三颗岛，嵌在南海的碧波间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三粒砂，嵌在祖国的身体里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，多像一只古老的蚌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海是她最柔软的部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从未曾舍弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将三粒砂放在体内磨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用每时每刻的呼吸和心跳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从未曾舍弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老的蚌，带着她的三粒砂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在又苦又咸的近代史里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉浮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折磨，苦难，漫长的孕育"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作珍珠的过程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个中国人都感到了痛"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}